<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Support — Nevarro Technologies</title>
<style>
  :root{--bg:#fbfbfd;--text:#1d1d1f;--muted:#6e6e73;--faint:#a1a1a6;--hairline:#e8e8ed;--accent:#5e8bff;--card:#fff}
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark){
    :root{--bg:#0d0d10;--text:#f5f5f7;--muted:#a1a1a6;--faint:#6e6e73;--hairline:#2a2a30;--accent:#7da2ff;--card:#1a1a1e}
  }
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
  body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"SF Pro Text","Helvetica Neue",Inter,Arial,sans-serif;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:1.2rem clamp(1.5rem,5vw,4rem)}
  .wordmark{font-size:.95rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--text);text-decoration:none}
  nav a{font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none}
  main{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem 5rem}
  h1{font-size:clamp(1.9rem,5vw,2.6rem);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.02em}
  h2{font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:600;margin:2.2rem 0 .6rem}
  p,li{color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;font-size:.96rem}
  ul,ol{padding-left:1.2rem;margin:.4rem 0}
  a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none}
  .box{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--hairline);border-radius:16px;padding:1.4rem 1.5rem;margin-top:1.5rem}
  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--hairline);text-align:center;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--faint);padding:1.2rem}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav><a class="wordmark" href="/">NEVARRO</a><a href="/">← Home</a></nav>
<main>
  <h1>Support & Escalation</h1>

  <div class="box">
    <p><strong>Primary support channel:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@nevarrotech.com">support@nevarrotech.com</a><br>
    First response within <strong>1 business day</strong> (Mon–Fri, IST). Active engagement clients also receive a direct line at kickoff.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>What support covers</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Questions about our consulting services and proposals</li>
    <li>Digital product purchases, downloads, and delivery issues</li>
    <li>Billing, invoices, receipts, and refund requests</li>
    <li>Bug reports for our tools (critical issues addressed within 2 business days)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Escalation path</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Level 1 — Support:</strong> email support@nevarrotech.com. Acknowledged within 1 business day; most issues resolved within 3 business days.</li>
    <li><strong>Level 2 — Founder review:</strong> if unresolved after 5 business days, reply with "ESCALATE" in the subject line. The founder personally reviews and responds within 2 business days.</li>
    <li><strong>Level 3 — Resolution:</strong> billing issues are resolved per our <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>; we aim to close every escalation within 10 business days.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Billing disputes</h2>
  <p>Before raising a chargeback with your bank or payment provider, please contact us — genuine billing errors are refunded promptly, and direct resolution is always faster.</p>
</main>
<footer>© 2026 Nevarro Technologies · <a href="/terms">Terms</a> · <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a></footer>
</body>
</html>
